The Future Awards Africa 2019 is happening right now, and the red carpet is bursting with Nigeria’s most inspiring youth, celebrities and brighest stars from business to the arts. This year’s Future Awards Africa is holding at the Balmoral Hall, Federal Palace Hotel, and it has quite the turnout of young entrepreneurs. Themed Nigeria’s New Tribe, the awards acknowledges inspiring young Nigerians aged 18-31 making a difference through social enterprise, social good, and creativity. The hosts of the night are Khafi Kareem and Taymesan. Stars such as Bolanle Olukanni, Elozonam, Diane, Toyin Abraham, Tolani Alli, Kie-Kie, Adesola Unuigbe, Jeff Bankz, Denrele Edun, Bimbo Ademoye, Gedoni, Khafi Kareem, Jeff and more have been spotted on the red carpet. See first photos below and head over to @bellanaijaonline for all the scoop. Oluwatosin Ogundadegbe aka The Style Infidel  Oluwatosin Ogundadegbe aka The Style Infidel  Steve chuks   @bimboademoye at The Future Awards Africa 2019. #TFAA2019 #TFAA #NigeriasNewTribe #BellaNaija bellanaija.com A post shared by  BellaNaija (@bellanaijaonline) on Nov 24, 2019 at 11:45am PST //www.instagram.com/embed.js   Just look that gorgeous smile on our very own Head of Content @adesola.au at The Future Awards Africa 2019. She's also a nominee! #TFAA2019 #TFAA #NigeriasNewTribe #BellaNaija bellanaija.com A post shared by  BellaNaija (@bellanaijaonline) on Nov 24, 2019 at 11:59am PST //www.instagram.com/embed.js  Taymesan  Elozonam  Diane  Chy Nwakanma  Khafi Kareem  Toyin Abraham  Mory Coco  Jeff  Gedoni The post First Look! Elozonam, Buimbo Ademoye, Adesola Ade-Unuigbe, Diane at The Future Awards Africa 2019 | #TFAA2019 appeared first on BellaNaija – Showcasing Africa to the world. Read today!. Source: Bella Naija